title: Eye on China, US lawmakers urge Biden to partner India on global vaccine supply - Hindustan Times
content:
1. Eye on China, US lawmakers urge Biden to partner India on global vaccine supply  Hindustan Times
  2. Lawmakers Urge Biden To Step Up Vaccine Diplomacy, Work With India To Strengthen Supply  News18
  3. US lawmakers urge Biden administration to ensure global supply of COVID-19 vaccines  The Financial Express
  4. View Full coverage on Google News
description: Pushing the US to take a leadership role in vaccine delivery, the lawmakers said that its allies are forced to use "sub-standard and ineffective" Chinese and Russian vaccines. The US lawmakers have lauded India's efforts in providing Covid vaccines to low-income countries.
